Product name: 3D Settlers of Catan resource tiles
Description:
Explore the realms of Catan in a whole new way with this hand sculpted resource set. 
The master tiles were hand sculpted in wax on a laser cut base and then molded with a high quality silicone.  The set is cast in a rugged urethane resin and will stand up to years of play and even the occasional "rage-quit."  Each tile is hand-painted with acrylics so the color may vary between sets but will be similar to what is pictured here. After painting, each tile is clear coated for long-lasting durability.
The original 3-4 player version includes the following:
3 - Brick Tiles
3 - Stone Tiles
4 - Wood Tiles
4 - Wheat Tiles
4 - Sheep Tiles
1 - Desert Tiles
The expanded 5-6 player edition includes:
5 - Brick Tiles
5 - Stone Tiles
6 - Wood Tiles
6 - Wheat Tiles
6 - Sheep Tiles
2 - Desert Tiles
NOTE: This is only one portion of the game - Settlers of Catan.  You will need to own a copy of the game in order to play.

Product name: Invisible Clip on Earrings, Clip-ons, Handmade DIY Findings for clip on dangle earrings, Wedding earrings, bridal earrings, Drop earrings
Description:
Handmade DIY FINDINGS to MAKE YOUR OWN invisible dangle clip on earrings. (non pierced earrings)
TOP QUALITY DIY FINDINGS to make your own dangle invisible clip on earrings. These are hard to break. HOWEVER, please do NOT open or twist them too much, they may loose their original shapes. 🍉 🍏 🍀 🍃🌴  
📪  🏠  Please, be sure that your Full Name & Mailing Address are Correct. Thank you!  📪  🏠
🍉 🌴  ITEM DESCRIPTIONS:  🍉 🌴
••• WEIGHT LIMIT: 4 grams (0.14 oz) on EACH SIDE. Please do NOT hang or connect any jewelry/craft components with the TOTAL weight of more than 4 grams (0.14 oz) to each resin clip. THESE CLIPS MAY NOT HOLD UP ANYTHING HEAVIER THAN 4 GRAMS (ON EACH SIDE). 
••• Available in 2 colors : Silver-Plated or Gold-Plated. Pearls on the back are acrylic Japanese Pearls (ivory color with subtle pink undertone, 4mm each)
These are ready to use. All you have to do is using jump rings  to connect your own jewelry/craft components to these clips to make your own dangle clip on earrings.
🌸  HOW  TO WEAR INVISIBLE CLIP ON EARRINGS? (VERY SIMPLE): 🌸
1] First, please see the 3rd (third photo from the left to right). The MOST IMPORTANT THING is do NOT open the resin clips too wide. They may loose their original shapes. 
2] Spread the resin clips SLIGHTLY ( Just enough to slip onto your earlobes). So when you release your fingers, the clips will snap back into their original shapes and pinch you earlobes securely.
WHAT ARE JAPANESE CLEAR RESIN CLIP ON EARRINGS? 
1) The clip-on parts are made of flexible and clear resin. So they look just like pierced earrings and are comfortable to wear for many hours. (However, wearing them to sleep is NOT recommended.)
2) They are designed to be precise and minimal to fit/hug your earlobes perfectly. As you can see from the photos, these Japanese invisible resin clip-ons are minimal and sophisticated. They are better than the clunky, big and obvious traditional metal clip-ons.
